{"tid":1535641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵各型號閘機","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:29:35.000Z","uid":1159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6f70f983d2296b1f4cdbcac9a3458194bed49f","tid":1535641,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrail.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2596%2598%25E6%25A9%259F&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=90c48381\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E9%96%98%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/7/7e/Cubic-Western_Data_gate_TWH.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20120525155337&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F7%2F7e%2FCubic-Western_Data_gate_TWH.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120525155337%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=3ee388e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「機霸自動系統」閘機，大部分設於觀塘綫及荃灣綫車站，攝於大窩口站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/b/b3/Alcatel_gate_TWH.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20120525160551&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fb3%2FAlcatel_gate_TWH.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120525160551%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=286329a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAlcatel（鐵路部分已被Thales收購）閘機，大部分設於港島綫車站，攝於大窩口站；而大窩口站的此款閘機已換成「機霸自動系統」閘機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/1/1b/MTR_HKGStn_WidwGate.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20110215155431&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F1%2F1b%2FMTR_HKGStn_WidwGate.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110215155431%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=c7e2f774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n供攜帶大型行李的乘客及殘疾人士乘客使用的開合式闊閘機，攝於香港站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/5/50/Tcl_oly_gates_2017.jpeg/revision/latest?cb=20180131134758&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F5%2F50%2FTcl_oly_gates_2017.jpeg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20180131134758%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=c530e364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東涌綫三棍閘機，攝於奧運站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/9/9c/MTR_TKL_NewGate.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20110215155223&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F9%2F9c%2FMTR_TKL_NewGate.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110215155223%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=7cc0fe42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n常見於將軍澳綫加建車站的新款開合式活板閘機，攝於調景嶺站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/8/88/KML_MetroStile_gate_TST.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20120525161756&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FKML_MetroStile_gate_TST.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120525161756%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=c272bf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMetroStile 伸縮活板閘機，攝於尖沙咀站（已於2018年換成Alcatel（鐵路部分已被Thales收購）閘機）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/e/ee/EAL_TAW_3stick_Gates.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20120226093917&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fee%2FEAL_TAW_3stick_Gates.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120226093917%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=a44e141e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東鐵綫三棍閘機，可見入閘部分向非收費區的一方拉長，攝於大圍站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/1/14/Gunnebo_gate_YUL.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20120623144116&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2F1%2F14%2FGunnebo_gate_YUL.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20120623144116%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=a34b6c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThales伸縮式活板閘機，攝於元朗站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/d/d7/DSC00340.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20161206114318&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd7%2FDSC00340.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20161206114318%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=a67d7ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘綫延綫Thales閘機，攝於何文田站"},{"pid":"84fc20d1c3ab72aaad40ca81bb8c5f3b7cb7013c","tid":1535641,"uid":133412,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"今日見到勁多人跨欄，果一跨，有世界級嘅技術，旁邊嘅人，亦有世界級嘅視若無睹，呢個Norm，真係無撚得頂。"},{"pid":"60ef1d3fd87c264d1dfe91c3713ecd27cbb0c223","tid":1535641,"uid":33392,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"三棍閘機得第一同第七款可以推開，其他要跳"},{"pid":"5a9fe2025ac4fdba1f4dfa788a65e70c1ba6e1e8","tid":1535641,"uid":103090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"港島線新站應該都係用最尾果款"},{"pid":"ed2c07c886afc01be7cc1deaf6872ba9b1e183b7","tid":1535641,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a9fe2025ac4fdba1f4dfa788a65e70c1ba6e1e8","tid":1535641,"uid":103090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"港島線新站應該都係用最尾果款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:23:27.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"32a880036edd8dc0e383611aad44dc16cbbe7f78","tid":1535641,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfc950351a7ba1277352d32e5a7a98d9c85da2a","tid":1535641,"uid":47222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"闊閘扮拍跟人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場907戰術：全部唔中途落車唔黑衫拖gip/接機 有車出車<br />\n到左就入返東涌再流水式入機場 或者機鐵唔落車<br />\n如果有必要情況下要set roadblock既set完即走做返市民<br />\n冇車走就商場shopping食飯唔洗心虛 等家長接<br />\n琴日證實青馬塞車會塞班警犬增援 不必過份擔心<br />\n<br />\n908 美領"},{"pid":"8f6cf641260f8212704a46777fe271d3749ac7d7","tid":1535641,"uid":307626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"諗緊可以整個全港黨鐵閘合集 提供每一個站用邊幾款閘嘅資訊 (可能有d多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d289bc6a8715d6bb1a1e4d958b52df7cf2658e9","tid":1535641,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"觀察所得，<br />\n其他入閘者係感覺佢地自己跳唔到，而且仲要快過佢嘟八達通。<br />\n回過神來，跳閘者已走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c64fb705249f1adbdf382e47680e8b2aad107d","tid":1535641,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f6cf641260f8212704a46777fe271d3749ac7d7","tid":1535641,"uid":307626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"諗緊可以整個全港黨鐵閘合集 提供每一個站用邊幾款閘嘅資訊 (可能有d多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"其實真係愈黎愈多人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0f8c5bf9ff8a1d9fa913fe662905e907ce5564","tid":1535641,"uid":103090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f6cf641260f8212704a46777fe271d3749ac7d7","tid":1535641,"uid":307626,"like":0,"disli